name: Adventurers
description:
Thank you all for downloading and reviewing this LoRA! I currently have plans to work on the next version, but there are still many challenges to overcome.

In addition, I found that sometimes certain themes can work better as standalone LoRAs rather than mixed LoRAs. As a pre-practice for the updated version, I have created some standalone LoRAs, including:


Angelic Wairrors
For divine armored characters such as Valkyrie, Priestesses, Paladin, Knight, and Angel.

Not Horny Pirate
For classic pirate.

Norse Viking
For Nordic style Viking Warrior and Berserker.

Non-Hentai Elf
For traditional fantasy elf characters such as Ranger, Warrior, Druid, and Priestess.

Thank you once again for your patience and support!
